			<h1>Projects</h1>
			<ul class="icons-ul">

	        <li><i class="icon-li icon-plus"></i><a href="https://github.com/patverga/plant_jones">Smart Plant / Sentiment Analysis</a> Arduino-based "smart" plant companion monitors moisture and sends alerts when thirsty. Built Twitter sentiment analysis model (Python, NumPy, scikit-learn) to re-tweet negative tweets when thirsty, and positive ones after being watered. </li>

	        <li><i class="icon-li icon-plus"></i> <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pemmaco.networkusage&hl=en">Android app</a> Designed and implemented an android app with <a href="http://people.cs.umass.edu/~strubell">Emma Strubell</a> to access the online game <a href="https://www.nationstates.net/">NationStates</a>. It is the most widely used app for the game with over 10,000 downloads.			
	</li>


</ul>
	


		
			<h1>Other Things About Pat</h1>
			
